    slug: "personality-test-science",
    title: "The Science Behind Personality Tests: What They Can and Cannot Tell You",
    excerpt: "From the MMPI to the MBTI to the Enneagram, personality tests have a complicated relationship with science. Here is what peer-reviewed research actually says — and how to use tests without being misled.",
    author: "Dr. Emily Hart",
